    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1941-01-21T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1941-01-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="680"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d680">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">700.00116 M.E./281</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador of the Soviet Union</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Umansky</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the Under Secretary of State</hi> (<persName
                        type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Welles</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-01-21">January 21,
                            1941</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear Mr. Under Secretary</hi>: I have the honor to
                    acknowledge receipt of your note of January 21, 1941 in which you inform me that
                    the Government of the United States of America has decided that the policies set
                    forth in the statement issued to the press by the President on December 2, 1939,
                    and generally referred to as the “moral embargo”, are no longer applicable to
                    the Union of Soviet Socialist Republics and that this decision is being
                    communicated to interested American manufacturers and exporters.</p>
                <p>I have taken note of the above communication and will not fail to report its
                    contents to my Government.</p>
                <p>I am [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>C. <hi rend="smallcaps">Oumansky</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
